authenticate the diff users(admins, dev, other users) to cluster we use kube configs


To update the current context:
>kubectl config use-context prod-user@production
So the above command will change the current context automatically in yaml file as well
Ex:
kubectl config --kubeconfig=/root/my-kube-config use-context research


The kubeconfig files are under
$HOME/.kube/config
To check further details
kubectl config -h
